Paper: hep-th/9610058

Date: 1996-10-09

Title: Verlinde Algebras and the Intersection Form on Vanishing Cycles

Authors: A.N. Varchenko,S.M.Gusein-Zade

Comments: latex file

We prove Zuber's conjecture establishing connections of the fusion rules ofthe $su(N)_k$ WZW model of conformal field theory and the intersection form onvanishing cycles of the associated fusion potential.